high_descs: Turn to the left, go forward till you get to the wall, turn right, and head towards the shelf.
Grab the plate off of the shelf.
Turn around, head toward the fridge, and face the fridge.
Open the fridge, place the plate in it, close the door, wait a bit, open the door, and take the plate out.
Turn to the right and head towards the shelf.
Place the plate on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place the plate in the fridge.

high_descs: Turn to the left and walk across the room, then turn right and walk across the room.
Take the black dish next to the red jar.
Turn around and walk to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the plate in it, then close the fridge for fridge for a few seconds before taking the plate out.
Turn to the right and walk across the room.
Put the plate on the shelf next to the red jar.
Turn left towards the fridge and then turn right towards the wooden shelves.
Pick up the plate from the shelves.
Turn around and walk towards the fridge.
Place the plate next to the tomato in the fridge, let it cool, and take it back out.
Turn right and head back towards the wooden shelves.
Place the plate to the left of the red vase on the shelves.
anns.task_desc: Warm up the plate on the shelves.
